Package io.github.angebagui.equilibre

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConnectivityNotifier.ConnectivityListener  
    CountCallback
    A CountCallback is used to run code after a EquilibreQuery is used to count objects matching a query in a background thread.
    DeleteCallback
    A DeleteCallback is used to run code after saving a EquilibreObject in a background thread.
    FindCallback<T extends EquilibreObject>
    A FindCallback is used to run code after a EquilibreQuery is used to fetch a list of EquilibreObjects in a background thread.
    FunctionalUtils.Function1<T,R>  
    FunctionalUtils.Function2<T>  
    GetCallback<T extends EquilibreObject>
    A GetCallback is used to run code after a EquilibreQuery is used to fetch a EquilibreObject in a background thread.
    ProgressCallback
    A ProgressCallback is used to get upload or download progress of a action.
    RefreshCallback<T extends EquilibreObject>
    A RefreshCallback is used to run code after refresh is used to update a EquilibreObject in a background thread.
    SaveCallback
    A SaveCallback is used to run code after saving a EquilibreObject in a background thread.
